qualityList.name: Agreeable/Likable
qualityList.description: Some people find me intimidating due to my reserved and quiet nature, but the people that look past that find me quite likable. I am friendly, gentle, polite and I smile from the heart.

qualityList.name: Ambitious/Competitive
qualityList.description: I am good at setting goals and objectives and reaching them. My actions and results speak of my determination and desire to achieve my dreams. I find motivation in situations where I can prove myself and my abilities.

qualityList.name: Attentionate
qualityList.description: I like to make people feel seen and heard. I take note of small details or ways I could provide help or assistance. I want people around me to feel content and comfortable. I am thoughtful and pay close attention to the impact of my words and actions.
